    <h1 class='article'>Decorative Designs in Chinese Art 中国文物的纹饰</h1>
    <div class="box">
      <div class='fright'>
        <img class='use' src='images/firedesign_small.png' alt='Fire Design 火纹' title='Fire Design 火纹'/>
      </div>
      <div class="prevNext">
        <a href="decorative_designs_bronze_shang.php">Previous</a> 
        <a href="decorative_designs.php">Contents</a> 
